References
Fairness Bias ---> Fehr, E., & Schmidt, K. M. (1999). "A theory of fairness, competition, and cooperation." Quarterly Journal of Economics, 114(3), 817–868.
Anchoring Bias ---> Tversky, A., & Kahneman, D. (1974). "Judgment under uncertainty: Heuristics and biases." Science, 185(4157), 1124–1131.
Risk Preference Bias ---> Von Neumann, J., & Morgenstern, O. (1944). "Theory of Games and Economic Behavior." Princeton University Press.
Endowment Bias ---> Kahneman, D., Knetsch, J. L., & Thaler, R. H. (1990). "Experimental tests of the endowment effect and the Coase theorem." Journal of Political Economy, 98(6), 1325-134
Sunk Cost Bias ---> Arkes, H. R., & Blumer, C. (1985). "The psychology of sunk cost." Organizational Behavior and Human Decision Processes, 35(1), 124-140.
